WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
â™ªThat dayâ™ª

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
â™ªNothing stays together foreverâ™ª

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
â™ªI've quit romanceâ™ª

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
â™ªWho hasn't failed againâ™ª

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
â™ªCrying in deathâ™ª

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
â™ªAnd in lifeâ™ª

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
â™ªEven nowâ™ª

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
â™ªWe keep learningâ™ª

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
â™ªIt's no surpriseâ™ª

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
â™ªBeing happy is so hardâ™ª

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
â™ªWeirdly, I became a role modelâ™ª

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
â™ªOn the day we met again, we said hiâ™ª

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
â™ªIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaintâ™ª

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
â™ªWho can do anything without regretâ™ª

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
â™ªI am all rightâ™ª

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
â™ªMay you live in peaceâ™ª

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
â™ªLet the world roarâ™ª

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
â™ªSounds like a carnivalâ™ª

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
â™ªBeing alive is never dullâ™ª

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
â™ªHow wonderful to be freeâ™ª

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
â™ªI became even better without youâ™ª

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
â™ªNothing can be perfectâ™ª

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
â™ªWe bless each other in painâ™ª

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
â™ªWe nod and smileâ™ª

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
â™ªMay we both be wellâ™ª

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.040 --> 01:43.533
=Episode 12=

01:55.811 --> 01:56.850
- Hello.
- Hello.

02:01.410 --> 02:02.171
Long time no see.

02:02.971 --> 02:03.690
Long time no see.

02:09.170 --> 02:09.811
Ms. Jiang,

02:09.840 --> 02:12.368
thank you for the support
in the first half of the year.

02:13.211 --> 02:14.051
Let me toast to you.

02:15.971 --> 02:16.771
Ms. Jiang.

02:17.850 --> 02:18.410
Hello,

02:18.730 --> 02:19.410
I'm Fang Lei.

02:24.251 --> 02:27.211
I'll make time to attend
the year-end gala.

02:28.371 --> 02:29.771
That would be greatly appreciated.

02:38.651 --> 02:39.130
Mr. Jiang.

02:43.931 --> 02:44.771
Fang Lei?

02:46.091 --> 02:46.850
Long time no see.

02:48.251 --> 02:49.130
When did you return?

02:49.811 --> 02:51.130
I've been back for a while.

02:51.771 --> 02:53.971
I've been meaning to visit you.

02:54.331 --> 02:55.450
But my father said

02:55.570 --> 02:57.091
you're mostly in New York now,

02:57.371 --> 02:58.771
rarely spending time in Jingzhou.

03:00.410 --> 03:01.570
I was busy earlier,

03:02.211 --> 03:03.931
but recently,

03:04.290 --> 03:05.410
my work has stabilized.

03:06.850 --> 03:07.931
Let's catch up when free.

03:09.211 --> 03:09.771
Sure.

03:17.251 --> 03:17.850
Excuse me.

03:18.570 --> 03:20.730
Do you have tomato sauce and honey?

03:24.010 --> 03:24.880
What are these for?

03:25.690 --> 03:26.570
Tomato juice

03:27.971 --> 03:29.771
mixed with honey.

03:30.331 --> 03:31.811
It helps with hangovers.

03:33.811 --> 03:34.570
Does it work?

03:35.371 --> 03:36.211
I've tried it before.

03:40.651 --> 03:42.051
Let's go. We're late.

03:42.211 --> 03:42.811
Wait.

03:43.570 --> 03:45.730
Going to Maggie's later,
we'll both get drunk for sure.

03:46.091 --> 03:48.531
This is my secret hangover remedy.

03:49.610 --> 03:50.730
What is this?

03:50.811 --> 03:53.771
Tomato sauce mixed with honey.
Family recipe. Try it.

03:54.290 --> 03:56.531
- Does it work?
- Of course.

03:56.971 --> 03:57.371
Hurry.

03:59.472 --> 04:00.816
Don't leave until you drink it.

04:12.251 --> 04:13.010
Really?

04:14.491 --> 04:15.570
You are sure to drink a lot

04:15.610 --> 04:16.850
at today's social gathering.

04:20.211 --> 04:21.771
What if I get drunk?

04:23.250 --> 04:24.144
I'll take care of you.

04:24.930 --> 04:25.730
You said it.

04:37.771 --> 04:38.490
I'd feel bad.

04:38.531 --> 04:39.290
I can do it myself.

04:39.370 --> 04:40.091
No worries.

04:40.490 --> 04:42.490
Many guys are careless these days.

04:46.256 --> 04:47.088
Are you free later?

04:47.971 --> 04:48.651
Yes.

04:49.050 --> 04:50.331
What do you want?

04:51.248 --> 04:52.816
Let me introduce you to some friends.

04:53.891 --> 04:55.810
Great. It's my honor.

04:56.930 --> 04:57.610
Mr. Jiang,

04:58.170 --> 05:00.091
hurry up. We've been waiting.

05:00.850 --> 05:01.410
Got it.

05:03.610 --> 05:04.571
Have some food first.

05:04.891 --> 05:05.771
Come find me later.

05:11.651 --> 05:12.691
Make yourself a drink too.

05:14.704 --> 05:15.728
I'll be waiting for you.

05:27.011 --> 05:27.971
What are you doing here?

05:29.730 --> 05:31.211
I'm part of the New District project.

05:31.930 --> 05:34.610
And my father has ties
with the Jiang family.

05:35.211 --> 05:36.891
I've known Jiang Liang for years.

05:37.571 --> 05:38.531
I can be helpful here.

05:42.531 --> 05:43.730
Through this approach?

05:46.850 --> 05:48.050
You think I'm embarrassing?

05:54.250 --> 05:55.451
There are just too many people

05:55.490 --> 05:57.490
flocking to Jiang Liang to flatter him.

05:57.771 --> 05:59.490
He knows they want something

06:00.131 --> 06:01.771
and has got used to being fawned over.

06:02.531 --> 06:03.571
He doesn't even care.

06:05.490 --> 06:07.490
But my status differs from theirs.

06:08.250 --> 06:09.451
By showing humility,

06:10.730 --> 06:13.011
I become more valuable to him.

06:16.730 --> 06:17.771
What you offer him

06:18.531 --> 06:20.011
is just emotional validation.

06:21.370 --> 06:23.691
He'll only think of you for fun,

06:24.850 --> 06:26.571
but no real business collaboration.

06:29.211 --> 06:30.490
I'm not that ambitious.

06:31.370 --> 06:33.131
I just want to help our project.

06:34.250 --> 06:35.810
Even a bit more goodwill helps.

06:36.571 --> 06:38.490
Being a decoration or backdrop

06:39.091 --> 06:40.250
is fine by me.

06:41.410 --> 06:42.370
Don't worry about me.

06:43.131 --> 06:44.131
I'm doing this willingly.

06:51.691 --> 06:52.971
I'll head over now.

07:17.131 --> 07:18.331
How've you been, Ms. Jiang?

07:18.571 --> 07:19.971
- I'm doing great.
- Sis.

07:23.610 --> 07:26.451
Next time, let me visit your father.
It's been a long time.

07:26.531 --> 07:28.131
And my father also misses you a lot.

07:28.691 --> 07:29.410
Mr. Shen.

07:29.810 --> 07:31.571
I'll leave you two to chat.

07:31.691 --> 07:32.011
Okay.

07:33.771 --> 07:34.691
Hello, Ms. Jiang.

07:35.290 --> 07:36.930
I'm Shen Haoming from Jinda Group.

07:37.050 --> 07:37.840
Nice to meet you.

07:38.410 --> 07:40.011
I've long heard of you.
Nice to meet you.

07:42.850 --> 07:44.490
- This is one solution.
- Exactly.

07:44.531 --> 07:45.490
It's jammed.

07:45.571 --> 07:45.891
Jammed.

07:45.930 --> 07:46.331
Come on.

07:51.410 --> 07:51.971
Excuse me.

07:55.170 --> 07:55.730
Haoming.

07:58.771 --> 07:59.376
You're here.

07:59.730 --> 08:00.971
- Sorry, I'm late.
- It's okay.

08:03.170 --> 08:03.691
My wife,

08:03.810 --> 08:04.250
Xu Yan.

08:04.370 --> 08:04.810
Hello.

08:05.410 --> 08:07.451
Ms. Jiang from Yuanhang Fund.

08:08.490 --> 08:09.331
Hello, Ms. Jiang.

08:09.651 --> 08:10.290
I'm Xu Yan.

08:10.691 --> 08:12.050
Miss Xu, nice to meet you.

08:12.624 --> 08:14.011
You two continue. I've got a call.

08:14.091 --> 08:14.531
Okay.

08:20.930 --> 08:22.091
The fieldwork ran late today.

08:22.131 --> 08:24.571
I didn't have time to change.
Sorry for the improper attire.

08:26.091 --> 08:27.211
This vest is practical.

08:28.250 --> 08:29.370
It holds many essentials.

08:29.712 --> 08:30.960
Windproof and waterproof too.

08:31.571 --> 08:34.211
Fieldwork fears
unpredictable weather most.

08:34.850 --> 08:36.250
Once the equipment is affected,

08:36.811 --> 08:37.811
all efforts are wasted.

08:39.370 --> 08:40.451
You're truly professional.

08:41.650 --> 08:43.691
I always keep things in my vest.

08:44.291 --> 08:44.890
Pens,

08:45.691 --> 08:49.171
spare camera batteries,

08:49.571 --> 08:50.490
my phone,

08:51.811 --> 08:53.130
and voice recorder.

08:53.451 --> 08:54.331
- Xu Yan.
- Lots of things.

08:55.451 --> 08:56.411
There's a dance later.

08:57.331 --> 08:59.130
Your current outfit isn't appropriate.

09:00.171 --> 09:01.171
Go to my lounge.

09:01.850 --> 09:02.931
I have spare outfits there.

09:04.051 --> 09:04.850
Is this okay?

09:05.331 --> 09:06.171
Absolutely.

09:06.971 --> 09:07.890
Thank you so much.

09:09.171 --> 09:10.370
- Let's go.
- This way?

09:12.610 --> 09:14.130
I think my clothes should fit you.

09:14.971 --> 09:15.610
Definitely.

09:24.650 --> 09:25.331
Ms. Jiang.

09:28.010 --> 09:28.650
Thank you.

09:32.890 --> 09:33.571
It's beautiful.

09:34.650 --> 09:36.051
That necklace suits you too.

09:39.250 --> 09:42.411
Formal wear never feels like me.

09:42.650 --> 09:44.010
It's not like uniforms, comfy,

09:44.250 --> 09:45.331
not tight, and fells free.

09:47.530 --> 09:49.171
Don't just stand. Have a seat.

09:50.171 --> 09:50.691
Thanks.

09:55.411 --> 09:57.250
Mr. Shen is fortunate

09:57.610 --> 09:59.291
to have such a beautiful wife like you.

09:59.691 --> 10:00.650
You handle work well

10:01.171 --> 10:02.971
and even go with him
to evening banquets.

10:03.610 --> 10:04.610
A true helpmate.

10:05.890 --> 10:09.010
I don't want to be the woman
behind her husband.

10:11.890 --> 10:14.171
Exhaustively supporting him,

10:14.770 --> 10:16.370
managing his daily life,

10:16.411 --> 10:18.010
and handling his company affairs.

10:19.890 --> 10:21.291
I don't think I can manage that.

10:24.811 --> 10:27.770
But that's how women in our circle live.

10:28.730 --> 10:29.850
Having clawed my way up

10:29.890 --> 10:31.610
from the bottom,

10:33.171 --> 10:36.691
I prefer controlling everything myself.

10:37.171 --> 10:38.331
It gives me security

10:39.451 --> 10:41.051
rather than making me an appendage.

10:45.091 --> 10:46.890
I remember you once said,

10:47.850 --> 10:48.850
"Be your own ship,

10:49.730 --> 10:50.890
your own lighthouse,

10:52.770 --> 10:53.811
and your own shore."

10:58.010 --> 10:59.850
When I first read these lines,

11:01.890 --> 11:02.811
I was deeply touched.

11:06.451 --> 11:09.850
I can tell
you've researched me thoroughly.

11:13.411 --> 11:15.130
You know I've stayed single
all these years

11:15.890 --> 11:17.691
and dislike the dutiful wife narrative.

11:18.850 --> 11:20.291
You showed up in a uniform

11:21.010 --> 11:24.571
to mirror my reporter days

11:25.890 --> 11:26.850
and win my favor.

11:28.370 --> 11:28.850
Am I right?

11:34.890 --> 11:36.850
I guess hardly anyone these days

11:37.530 --> 11:40.091
would wear that kind of vest
for interviews.

11:45.211 --> 11:46.010
You're right.

11:49.250 --> 11:50.091
That's how it is.

11:52.770 --> 11:53.650
But it's okay.

11:54.610 --> 11:55.370
You succeeded.

11:57.171 --> 11:58.171
Because just now,

11:58.971 --> 12:02.650
I really saw my past self in you.

12:08.051 --> 12:09.571
I brought a gift for you.

12:15.971 --> 12:18.096
(Years Like Songs)

12:21.059 --> 12:22.960
(Journalist Photo Collection)

12:32.890 --> 12:35.130
I found these photos in the archives.

12:35.850 --> 12:36.730
They're quite old.

12:38.451 --> 12:40.331
When I first started working,

12:40.530 --> 12:42.650
I kept hearing
about your legendary stories.

12:45.931 --> 12:47.370
(Amazing Intangible Heritage)
But you had already left by then.

12:47.650 --> 12:48.250
So,

12:49.490 --> 12:50.650
that's a pity we never met.

12:52.171 --> 12:53.610
But ever since then,

12:55.971 --> 12:57.370
you've always been my role model.

13:08.610 --> 13:10.610
I'm sorry about earlier.

13:12.691 --> 13:13.890
If everything just now

13:13.931 --> 13:15.091
was some kind of act,

13:16.571 --> 13:17.770
I want you to know this gift

13:18.811 --> 13:19.770
is completely genuine.

13:23.331 --> 13:24.091
Thank you.

13:25.571 --> 13:26.411
This gift...

13:27.411 --> 13:28.331
I really like it.

13:37.530 --> 13:39.051
- Come on.
- Cheers!

13:43.130 --> 13:44.370
Let me introduce, everyone.

13:45.331 --> 13:47.291
She's Fang Lei.
Just returned from abroad.

13:48.411 --> 13:49.691
This is my good friend,

13:49.811 --> 13:50.610
Chen Heng.

13:51.811 --> 13:52.691
- Nice to meet you.
- Heng.

13:55.411 --> 13:56.890
This is also my good friend,

13:57.171 --> 13:58.411
- Wu Chang.
- Oh, stop it.

13:58.571 --> 13:59.051
Chang.

14:01.850 --> 14:03.451
This is another recent returnee,

14:03.971 --> 14:05.370
- Wang Hao.
- Hi, Hao.

14:09.250 --> 14:09.770
Bottoms up!

14:13.370 --> 14:14.530
- Fill it up.
- Top up her glass.

14:14.971 --> 14:16.931
- Absolutely.
- Great drinking skills.

14:19.890 --> 14:20.691
Yun.

14:21.571 --> 14:23.250
Kriya, long time no see.

14:23.571 --> 14:24.211
Yeah,

14:24.331 --> 14:25.370
our last meeting

14:25.411 --> 14:26.890
was two years ago

14:26.971 --> 14:28.130
in New York's Central Park.

14:28.971 --> 14:30.291
You finally came back.

14:30.730 --> 14:32.931
The domestic opportunities
brought me back.

14:33.091 --> 14:36.010
About the collaboration we discussed,
we must make it happen this time.

14:36.010 --> 14:37.931
We must sign the contract, okay?

14:37.971 --> 14:39.931
All the postponed gatherings
must also happen now.

14:44.130 --> 14:45.010
What are you doing?

14:45.051 --> 14:46.411
We're drinking, waiting for you.

14:47.171 --> 14:48.850
- Come on.
- Let's drink together.

14:48.850 --> 14:49.370
Bottoms up?

14:50.091 --> 14:50.411
Cheers!

14:50.451 --> 14:50.931
Come on.

14:52.811 --> 14:53.971
Am I interrupting?

14:56.451 --> 14:58.091
Xu Yan's husband.

14:58.530 --> 15:00.291
Mr. Shen from Jinda Group.

15:01.490 --> 15:02.130
Hello, Mr. Shen.

15:02.171 --> 15:02.530
Hello.

15:02.610 --> 15:03.472
I've heard so much.

15:03.691 --> 15:05.010
You go ahead.

15:05.051 --> 15:05.890
I'll leave now.

15:10.091 --> 15:11.931
This gown looks stunning.

15:12.051 --> 15:12.571
Is it?

15:13.691 --> 15:14.971
Ms. Jiang picked it.

15:15.091 --> 15:16.931
Without your help, I'd be lost.

15:17.730 --> 15:20.400
I had a great conversation with Xu Yan.
We feel like old friends.

15:20.571 --> 15:21.171
That's good.

15:21.850 --> 15:23.331
Would Xu Yan have the honor

15:23.490 --> 15:25.051
to do an exclusive interview with you?

15:29.370 --> 15:31.571
Consider it her debut opportunity.

15:34.650 --> 15:36.091
What's your angle?

15:40.091 --> 15:41.091
Typical elite interviews

15:41.691 --> 15:43.451
just ask successful people

15:43.490 --> 15:44.610
how they view success.

15:45.411 --> 15:47.411
But if you accept my interview,

15:47.490 --> 15:48.451
I want to explore

15:48.890 --> 15:51.770
what role your journalism past played

15:52.610 --> 15:53.650
in your entrepreneurship.

15:55.331 --> 15:56.051
Interested?

16:00.016 --> 16:00.931
Let's walk and talk.

16:01.411 --> 16:01.850
Let's go.

16:16.530 --> 16:17.211
Wipe your mouth.

16:33.890 --> 16:37.051
My deal with Yuanhang Fund is settled.

16:37.730 --> 16:40.130
You don't need
to flatter Jiang Liang anymore.

16:50.490 --> 16:51.890
The collaboration has just begun.

16:52.691 --> 16:54.051
There's a long journey ahead.

16:56.051 --> 16:57.650
Any connection that's beneficial to you,

16:58.490 --> 16:59.730
I'll spare no effort

17:00.451 --> 17:01.650
to maintain it well for you.

17:10.010 --> 17:13.770
I think I'm really useless.

17:16.770 --> 17:20.050
Xu Yan is truly impressive.

17:21.211 --> 17:21.891
She's beautiful,

17:23.010 --> 17:23.691
smart,

17:25.131 --> 17:26.090
and capable.

17:27.570 --> 17:30.371
Jiang Yun is such an aloof person.

17:31.931 --> 17:34.211
I don't even dare to approach her.

17:36.770 --> 17:37.770
Yet Xu Yan convinced her

17:37.851 --> 17:39.010
with just a few words.

17:39.730 --> 17:42.290
I truly am becoming more aware

17:44.451 --> 17:45.891
of why she's so captivating to you.

17:50.691 --> 17:52.131
I really can't compare to her.

18:22.931 --> 18:25.010
Drink some warm milk
to soothe your stomach.

18:29.530 --> 18:31.010
Thanks, Haoming.

18:46.891 --> 18:48.691
Mr. Shen, I'll take her home first.

19:23.010 --> 19:24.691
I just wanted to check
if you have a fever.

19:26.651 --> 19:27.851
There's nothing between us.

19:30.050 --> 19:31.050
Don't think being nice

19:32.010 --> 19:33.072
will make me fall for you.

19:35.971 --> 19:36.851
My heart

19:37.851 --> 19:39.451
belongs solely to Shen Haoming.

19:41.050 --> 19:42.131
It was true before,

19:43.211 --> 19:44.851
and will remain so.

19:45.616 --> 19:46.864
Why put yourself through this?

19:48.250 --> 19:49.451
He has a wife and family.

19:50.611 --> 19:51.891
They have a loving marriage.

19:52.611 --> 19:54.411
There's no possibility between you two.

19:56.611 --> 19:58.050
You don't need to worry about that.

19:59.931 --> 20:01.050
Between him and me,

20:02.090 --> 20:03.770
there's an unbreakable bond.

20:05.971 --> 20:07.248
Outsiders wouldn't understand.

20:16.931 --> 20:17.411
Let's go.

20:18.971 --> 20:20.171
- Where to?
- Wait.

20:26.330 --> 20:27.770
You feel something's missing too.

21:04.290 --> 21:05.530
Haoming, come on.

21:14.730 --> 21:15.290
Haoming.

21:19.824 --> 21:20.912
What are you doing here?

21:22.570 --> 21:23.611
Why aren't you asleep yet?

21:26.171 --> 21:27.451
I thought about it a lot,

21:27.490 --> 21:28.570
and still want to ask you.

21:31.611 --> 21:33.451
About you making me interview Ms. Jiang,

21:34.250 --> 21:35.490
why didn't you ask me first?

21:38.330 --> 21:40.131
I just became a host recently.

21:41.651 --> 21:42.971
I'm still inexperienced.

21:44.250 --> 21:45.411
If I ended up ruining

21:46.371 --> 21:48.050
your collaboration, what then?

21:48.651 --> 21:49.851
You're my wife.

21:50.810 --> 21:51.810
You have what it takes.

21:53.730 --> 21:55.770
Didn't you perform well today?

21:57.171 --> 21:58.131
I'm very satisfied.

21:59.371 --> 22:00.730
Stop overthinking.

22:01.570 --> 22:02.371
Go to sleep now.

22:07.131 --> 22:07.891
Mr. Shen,

22:08.290 --> 22:09.411
I'll be straight.

22:10.810 --> 22:12.976
I asked to meet today to discuss

22:13.220 --> 22:15.810
your proposed strategic partnership
for the New District project.

22:17.490 --> 22:19.280
I'm looking forward to it.
Please go ahead.

22:20.691 --> 22:23.131
I had a wonderful conversation
with your wife yesterday.

22:24.490 --> 22:25.570
However, many companies

22:25.611 --> 22:27.131
are currently seeking our investment.

22:27.856 --> 22:29.360
Four have made the preliminary list.

22:29.810 --> 22:31.411
Although you're among them,

22:31.730 --> 22:32.931
I won't choose you

22:32.971 --> 22:34.851
simply because your wife

22:35.171 --> 22:37.490
shares my profession or interests.

22:38.211 --> 22:38.810
Understood.

22:39.611 --> 22:40.371
Mr. Shen,

22:41.010 --> 22:42.570
my sister speaks diplomatically,

22:44.090 --> 22:45.171
but I'll be blunt.

22:46.290 --> 22:47.250
Frankly speaking,

22:47.770 --> 22:49.090
you're not the best candidate.

22:50.211 --> 22:51.971
Without backing from the parent company,

22:52.090 --> 22:54.770
going solo is too risky
without safety nets.

22:56.171 --> 22:57.490
So why should we choose you?

23:01.211 --> 23:03.090
Regarding your mention
of my wife earlier,

23:03.730 --> 23:05.090
she's a public figure

23:05.730 --> 23:07.651
whose reputation is built
on authenticity

23:08.090 --> 23:09.090
and credibility.

23:10.290 --> 23:11.851
Any dishonesty

23:12.770 --> 23:14.971
would be devastating

23:15.651 --> 23:17.490
for both our careers.

23:18.770 --> 23:20.131
That's why

23:20.371 --> 23:22.851
we must be more authentic,

23:23.171 --> 23:24.050
more responsible,

23:24.371 --> 23:25.211
and more meticulous.

23:26.971 --> 23:28.250
You're quite articulate.

23:29.090 --> 23:30.451
In just a few sentences,

23:31.131 --> 23:32.411
it's all to your advantage.

23:40.211 --> 23:41.530
Last night,

23:41.570 --> 23:43.730
we were photographed together

23:43.730 --> 23:44.810
(Shining Business, Dazzling Banquet)
at the banquet.

23:48.211 --> 23:49.090
This morning,

23:50.211 --> 23:51.570
(Xunchao Hot Search)
it's already trending.

23:52.490 --> 23:53.730
But most importantly...

23:57.091 --> 23:58.971
(Jinda Group, Yuanhang Fund, Stocks)

23:58.971 --> 24:01.770
Both Jinda and Yuanhang's stocks
are rising.

24:05.651 --> 24:06.611
To be honest,

24:07.730 --> 24:09.131
the current investment for me

24:09.651 --> 24:11.490
happens to also involve four companies.

24:12.250 --> 24:13.931
So why should I choose Yuanhang?

24:17.211 --> 24:18.250
I'll wait for your call.

24:28.730 --> 24:29.530
Interesting.

24:41.691 --> 24:43.411
Weren't you supposed
to meet clients today?

24:44.171 --> 24:46.490
I finished early and wanted
to have lunch with you.

24:55.131 --> 24:55.891
This is for you.

24:59.330 --> 25:00.530
Why are you giving me a gift?

25:05.851 --> 25:07.330
Isn't this too expensive?

25:09.330 --> 25:10.451
I have good news.

25:10.851 --> 25:13.290
Yuanhang and I
have reached a cooperation.

25:14.651 --> 25:15.851
So that means

25:16.090 --> 25:18.651
the New District project
can move forward.

25:19.611 --> 25:21.691
Convincing them wasn't easy.

25:22.451 --> 25:24.530
Luckily, I have a capable wife.

25:25.891 --> 25:27.330
This deal couldn't have been done

25:27.730 --> 25:28.770
without you.

25:29.611 --> 25:31.131
Do you think I don't realize that?

25:32.131 --> 25:34.131
It's not because I got along
with Ms. Jiang

25:34.171 --> 25:35.611
that she chose to work with you.

25:36.250 --> 25:38.651
My role was just to create

25:38.730 --> 25:40.050
a harmonious communication space.

25:40.290 --> 25:43.171
The real motivator was mutual benefits.

25:44.211 --> 25:45.691
So the one who made this happen

25:46.090 --> 25:47.931
is you, not me.

25:49.050 --> 25:50.570
Such an expensive gift

25:51.691 --> 25:52.691
makes me feel unworthy.

25:58.730 --> 26:01.131
As my wife,
you should get used to gifts.

26:02.371 --> 26:03.891
Get in the car. Let's go.

26:23.570 --> 26:24.290
It suits you well.

26:43.090 --> 26:44.816
(The more valuable Haoming's gifts are,)

26:45.570 --> 26:47.171
(the deeper my guilt grows.)

26:48.490 --> 26:50.211
(They keep reminding me)

26:51.290 --> 26:52.250
(that can these lies)

26:53.250 --> 26:55.611
(truly withstand sunlight?)

26:56.899 --> 27:00.816
(Shanxi Jinxing Bank)

27:01.971 --> 27:02.931
What's for dinner?

27:02.931 --> 27:04.570
My mom went to Jingzhou for orthopedics.

27:04.570 --> 27:05.490
Guess who we saw there?

27:05.530 --> 27:07.891
- Who?
- Mr. Lin's fiancÃ©e, Qiao Lin.

27:08.211 --> 27:09.250
They just broke up,

27:09.411 --> 27:10.611
and she's already upgraded.

27:11.050 --> 27:12.211
The chief orthopedic doctor

27:12.411 --> 27:13.451
is talented and handsome.

27:13.611 --> 27:14.211
You're right.

27:14.371 --> 27:16.651
Maybe she was already seeing him

27:16.691 --> 27:18.010
- before breaking up with Mr. Lin.
- Exactly!

27:23.891 --> 27:24.651
What's wrong?

27:25.290 --> 27:26.611
My heart hurts.

27:35.971 --> 27:37.090
This is orthopedics.

27:37.931 --> 27:38.931
If it's heart issues,

27:38.931 --> 27:39.891
we can't help here.

27:40.250 --> 27:42.611
Cancel your registration
and visit cardiology instead.

27:42.971 --> 27:44.451
Stop pretending.

27:45.171 --> 27:46.611
You must tell me today

27:47.131 --> 27:48.570
where you're hiding Qiao Lin.

27:49.730 --> 27:50.971
Let me make this clear.

27:51.530 --> 27:52.851
Hiding won't work.

27:53.211 --> 27:54.851
I'm persistent.

27:55.611 --> 27:57.691
I'm using my remaining sanity

27:57.851 --> 27:59.090
to be civil with you.

28:00.090 --> 28:01.611
Don't make me expose

28:01.691 --> 28:03.131
all your dirty secrets.

28:04.211 --> 28:06.090
First, I have no secrets.

28:06.411 --> 28:08.371
Second, leave if you're not here
for treatment.

28:08.931 --> 28:10.411
Stop wasting medical resources.

28:12.530 --> 28:15.451
I've noticed you're thick-skinned.

28:15.851 --> 28:17.651
You seduce someone's fiancÃ©e.

28:18.171 --> 28:20.171
When the groom came looking for you,

28:20.211 --> 28:21.770
you still act innocent.

28:22.570 --> 28:25.050
You've kept me awake at night.

28:25.411 --> 28:27.010
Don't think you can brush this off

28:27.090 --> 28:28.451
with a few words. No way!

28:29.330 --> 28:31.770
Are you here for treatment or not?
If not, just leave.

28:32.330 --> 28:33.971
You're enabling evil, you know?

28:34.131 --> 28:35.770
He's a homewrecker!

28:36.131 --> 28:38.010
Liu, call security.

28:38.411 --> 28:39.851
Go ahead.

28:39.971 --> 28:41.010
Get your dean here.

28:41.171 --> 28:42.931
Let your leaders and colleagues see

28:42.971 --> 28:44.050
what a morally corrupt

28:44.131 --> 28:45.530
- homewrecking man...
- Lin Tao!

28:58.891 --> 29:00.651
- What do you want?
- What now?

29:01.570 --> 29:03.250
I finally catch you red-handed.

29:03.530 --> 29:04.611
What did I say?

29:04.971 --> 29:06.891
Right after leaving me,
you've found someone new.

29:07.211 --> 29:07.810
Lin,

29:08.530 --> 29:09.931
just be blunt to me today.

29:10.730 --> 29:12.691
Were you together
behind my back long ago?

29:12.770 --> 29:13.490
Are you done yet?

29:13.810 --> 29:14.770
This is a hospital.

29:16.131 --> 29:17.090
Didn't you always claim

29:17.090 --> 29:18.451
you're educated high-class person?

29:18.451 --> 29:20.611
You're making a scene here,
disturbing other patients.

29:20.611 --> 29:22.171
Is this what you call high-class?

29:22.770 --> 29:24.891
Since when did you learn
to twist the truth?

29:26.010 --> 29:27.570
You want to lecture me about manners?

29:28.211 --> 29:30.371
Yu Yiming destroyed families.

29:30.411 --> 29:31.411
That makes him classy?

29:31.730 --> 29:34.330
A morally corrupt person like him
can't possibly be a good doctor.

29:34.530 --> 29:36.691
Now you're just spouting nonsense.

29:37.131 --> 29:38.290
How did he destroy families?

29:38.480 --> 29:39.770
Whose family did he destroy?

29:39.971 --> 29:41.411
Did we ever make a family?

29:42.211 --> 29:43.730
We broke up ages ago, okay?

29:43.971 --> 29:46.090
We have zero connection now.

29:46.330 --> 29:49.371
If you keep harassing me like this,
it counts as harassment, you know?

29:49.570 --> 29:50.211
Wait.

29:50.891 --> 29:51.851
I'm begging you.

29:52.050 --> 29:53.211
Just come back with me.

29:54.050 --> 29:55.411
I came specifically to get you.

29:56.250 --> 29:57.211
Hopeless.

29:57.570 --> 29:59.250
I don't want to speak to you at all now.

29:59.371 --> 29:59.931
Get out.

30:00.330 --> 30:02.651
Then tell me where you live now.
Is he treating you well?

30:04.570 --> 30:06.371
No. I'm sorry.

30:06.371 --> 30:07.184
(Advanced Mathematics)

30:10.290 --> 30:11.651
You're attending adult college?

30:11.770 --> 30:14.050
- What's it to you?
- Just to be worthy of Yu Yiming?

30:15.211 --> 30:16.250
Are you insane?

30:16.611 --> 30:17.770
What twisted logic is this?

30:18.250 --> 30:20.131
My studies have nothing to do with him.

30:20.490 --> 30:22.131
Your mental gymnastics amaze me.

30:23.691 --> 30:25.010
Still lying to me, huh?

30:25.931 --> 30:26.611
Lin.

30:27.371 --> 30:29.851
You used to complain
that I shouldn't despise you.

30:30.490 --> 30:31.290
But now?

30:32.330 --> 30:34.530
Yu Yiming is the one who actually

30:34.570 --> 30:35.691
despise you.

30:36.330 --> 30:38.250
He knows you hate studying,

30:38.611 --> 30:40.090
and you're not cut out for it.

30:40.490 --> 30:42.611
Yet for his own pride,
he forces you to study.

30:42.691 --> 30:44.171
This is emotional manipulation.

30:44.451 --> 30:46.171
I might have said things,

30:46.330 --> 30:47.171
but in my heart,

30:47.290 --> 30:50.330
I've always accepted your lack
of education and common sense.

30:53.330 --> 30:54.490
Well, thank you.

30:55.411 --> 30:56.931
Thanks for accepting me

30:57.090 --> 30:58.931
as some uneducated, brainless woman.

30:59.010 --> 31:00.131
I'm so grateful.

31:00.211 --> 31:01.611
- How can I ever thank you enough?
- Qiao Lin! Qiao Lin!

31:02.931 --> 31:04.090
No fighting in the hospital.

31:04.131 --> 31:05.010
Talk it out properly.

31:08.770 --> 31:11.290
Yu Yiming, this doesn't concern you.

31:11.490 --> 31:13.171
Even if she kills me today,

31:13.290 --> 31:14.851
you have no right to interfere.

31:15.770 --> 31:18.050
Because you'll never measure up to me.

31:18.770 --> 31:20.330
Let me be blunt.

31:20.891 --> 31:22.290
Qiao Lin was my first love.

31:24.010 --> 31:25.651
No one's relationship can compare

31:25.691 --> 31:26.770
to what we had.

31:30.290 --> 31:31.931
- He's crazy.
- I'm not crazy.

31:40.530 --> 31:42.730
These were all selected
by Mr. Shen for you.

31:42.851 --> 31:43.730
Happy birthday.

31:45.891 --> 31:46.651
Thank you.

31:46.931 --> 31:47.611
We'll leave now.

31:47.651 --> 31:48.171
Thank you.

31:52.483 --> 31:54.544
(To Yan: Happy Birthday, 6 PM, Haoming)

32:02.651 --> 32:04.770
(Meet at Agave at 6 PM)

32:11.290 --> 32:11.691
Okay.

32:13.219 --> 32:19.728
(Fang Lei Calling)

32:20.211 --> 32:20.651
Hello?

32:20.891 --> 32:24.770
Time flies. He's grown so tall.

32:27.536 --> 32:28.688
Who allowed you to meet him?

32:29.250 --> 32:30.931
I miss him terribly.

32:31.290 --> 32:32.090
Where are you now?

32:40.770 --> 32:42.290
- You're here?
- Who allowed you to meet him?

32:45.851 --> 32:47.810
I couldn't help myself today.

32:48.330 --> 32:49.691
So I went to see him.

32:51.290 --> 32:54.530
He looks just like me.

32:55.451 --> 32:58.971
This is your final warning.
Don't cross the line again.

33:02.611 --> 33:03.691
Just kidding.

33:06.290 --> 33:09.411
It's Yan's birthday today, right?

33:23.152 --> 33:25.451
Mr. Shen's not here.
He asked you to wait in the backyard.

33:25.451 --> 33:26.290
He'll be back soon.

33:26.490 --> 33:27.171
Okay. Thank you.

33:27.250 --> 33:28.010
I'll head off work.

34:40.731 --> 34:44.331
Did I interrupt
your little romantic time?

34:45.411 --> 34:46.331
I'm sorry.

34:49.490 --> 34:50.371
It seems

34:50.771 --> 34:53.291
you still care about us deep down.

34:57.971 --> 34:59.811
- If you leave, I'll really go meet him.
- Don't you dare!

35:04.610 --> 35:07.371
I don't need anyone's permission

35:07.411 --> 35:08.731
before meeting him.

35:14.771 --> 35:16.451
We're related by blood.

35:18.170 --> 35:21.251
You and I are family bound by ties

35:21.331 --> 35:22.690
that can never be severed.

35:24.331 --> 35:26.731
But I don't understand
why you had to marry someone

35:26.771 --> 35:28.010
completely unrelated to us.

35:32.650 --> 35:35.170
Why couldn't you wait for me?

35:41.610 --> 35:42.050
Fang Lei.

35:45.050 --> 35:46.610
For your sister's sake,

35:47.731 --> 35:48.570
please let me go.

35:53.971 --> 35:55.291
Then I'll go find my sister.

36:00.690 --> 36:01.490
What's that?

36:03.490 --> 36:04.090
Put it down!

36:07.523 --> 36:08.368
(Acetagastrodin Tablets)

36:49.090 --> 36:49.811
Yan.

36:50.610 --> 36:51.210
Chen Lin,

36:51.971 --> 36:53.490
do you know where Shen Haoming is?

36:54.000 --> 36:55.811
Mr. Shen said
he has an appointment with you.

36:56.170 --> 36:57.731
He left work early for his studio.

37:01.971 --> 37:02.851
Never mind. Thanks.

37:23.130 --> 37:24.010
You're back.

37:27.376 --> 37:29.936
You didn't answer the phone.
I thought something happened to you.

37:30.291 --> 37:30.891
I'm fine.

37:31.490 --> 37:33.291
Shifeng and Jinda
are signing a contract.

37:33.331 --> 37:36.050
There was an urgent meeting,
so I put my phone on silent.

37:38.010 --> 37:40.971
Have you eaten? Are you hungry?
I make you a midnight snack, okay?

37:41.610 --> 37:43.371
I'm not hungry. I had a snack earlier.

37:50.650 --> 37:51.971
You must've been waiting long.

37:52.851 --> 37:54.851
It's okay. I know
you had urgent matters.

37:55.050 --> 37:56.210
- It's okay.
- I'm sorry.

37:57.530 --> 37:58.490
Happy birthday.

38:01.210 --> 38:03.451
I'll take a shower first.
Then we'll have cake together.

38:03.931 --> 38:04.371
Okay.

39:19.130 --> 39:20.010
What happened to her?

39:20.891 --> 39:21.771
I don't know, either.

39:22.210 --> 39:25.811
She had an accident while diving.

39:27.650 --> 39:28.650
Does Mr. Fang know yet?

39:30.050 --> 39:31.650
My father's almost here.

